node.contents: On none of the threads do I see my code, so I am confused as to how this ANR can be happening due to my own code. The only code I see from a library that I installed was Google Analytics (GA) which you can see titled "GAThread". Could that be the culprit? If so, could someone explain how I could deduce that from this report?
